Few people know about the mailbox conspiracy, in which all mailboxes of the world are plotting to destroy humanity. This video will tell you all the things you missed, such as how various events in the Cold War, including Ping Pong Diplomacy, threats of thermonuclear war, and Stratetic Arms Limitation Talks I and II, are related to the conspiracy. We will also explain how to prepare for your impending doom because it is impossible to prevent or delay the fate that the mailboxes have already determined.
